1. Download Rogers.js from the downloads page, and place it somewhere convenient in your plugin or portal installation.

2. Include Rogers.js using <script src="URL_TO_ROGERS_JS" type="text/javascript"/>

3. Enjoy!

Getting Involved
This project is a joint effort among Liferay community members, to provide a useful JavaScript Library 
for Liferay Frontend developers. As such, we are always looking for new volunteers who can help with the 
project's goals! Visit the overview page and contact the founder to get involved!